text:
@Keir_Starmer Keir, the coronavirus is still with us. 

Yes, the nation seems to have come together - but on Bournemouth beach.

This government’s confusing programme will kill. It has already killed 65,000 of us.

The private-contracted Test+Trace is appalling.

Your tweet is ill advised.
